%% Model Registry - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4/model-registry.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client/Dashboard
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS
    participant Proxy as model-registry proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8sAPI as K8s API Server<br/>HTTPS
    participant Controller as InferenceService<br/>Controller
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant BFF as UI BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Catalog as model-catalog server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PgDB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KServe as KServe Init Container
    participant CSI as mr-storage-initializer
    participant Storage as Model Storage (S3/OCI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>Istio: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Istio AuthorizationPolicy
    Istio->>Proxy: Forward (mTLS STRICT)
    Proxy->>DB: INSERT model metadata<br/>TLS 1.2+ (configurable)<br/>DB credentials
    DB-->>Proxy: Result
    Proxy-->>Istio: 201 Created
    Istio-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over K8sAPI,Controller: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync (Controller)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService CR<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Proxy: GET/POST inference service state<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Proxy-->>Controller: Registry state
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update ISVC labels<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Browser,Catalog: Flow 3: UI Request Flow
    Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/model_registry<br/>K8s Bearer Token
    BFF->>Proxy: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/*<br/>Istio mTLS
    Proxy-->>BFF: Model data
    BFF->>Catalog: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/models<br/>Istio mTLS
    Catalog-->>BFF: Catalog data
    BFF-->>Browser: Aggregated response

    Note over KServe,Storage: Flow 4: Model Download (CSI Storage Initializer)
    KServe->>CSI: Init container with model-registry:// URI
    CSI->>Proxy: GET model artifact metadata<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    Proxy-->>CSI: Artifact location (S3/OCI URL)
    CSI->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Storage credentials
    Storage-->>CSI: Model files

    Note over Catalog,HFHub: Flow 5: Catalog Model Sync
    Catalog->>HFHub: GET models/metadata<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>HF_API_KEY (optional)
    HFHub-->>Catalog: Model catalog data
    Catalog->>PgDB: Upsert catalog entries<br/>PostgreSQL 5432/TCP<br/>DB credentials
